Package hw4

Class SimpleElement

java.lang.Object
api.AbstractElement
hw4.SimpleElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
Drawable
Direct Known Subclasses:
MovingElement, VanishingElement
public class SimpleElement extends AbstractElement
Minimal concrete extension of AbstractElement. The update method in this implementation just increments the frame count.
Author:
Nicholas Jacobs
